text: Diadelia albomarmorata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1965.BioLib.cz - Diadelia albomarmorata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1965 Category:Taxa named by Stephan von Breuning
